keyPolicies.policyDescription: Labour will create a National Education Service to make sure everyone in Canterbury and Whitstable can benefit from world-class education
Labour will make sure every worker earns a real living wage of £10 an hour and we will invest in skills for Canterbury and Whitstable

issues.brexitEurope: Labour will fight to stop the disastrous and chaotic No Deal Brexit.
issues.economy: Labour will make sure every worker earns a real living wage of £10 an hour and we will invest in skills for Canterbury and Whitstable.
issues.education: Labour will create a National Education Service to make sure everyone in Canterbury and Whitstable can benefit from world-class education.
issues.health: Labour will fight for the NHS services at Kent & Canterbury Hospital and other local services.

housing.content: Labour will build the homes we need and make radical reforms of the rental sector to protect tenants.
